Dhanlaxmi Says Allegations of Improper Accounting Are Baseless

-- B y   A n t o   A n t o n y
-- 
2011-10-11T12:47:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/dhanlaxmi-says-allegations-of-improper-accounting-are-baseless.html
Dhanlaxmi Bank Ltd. (DHLBK)  said allegations
by a former employee’s association for improper accounting at
the lender were “baseless,” according to an e-mailed statement
today.  The worker’s group accounts for less than 10 percent of the
bank’s staff, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anto Antony in New Delhi at 
 aantony1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Abhay Singh at 
 abhaysingh@bloomberg.net  